snippet.title: The Disney Afternoon Collection - TaleSpin Retrospective
snippet.description:
Join us as we look back at Baloo's origins, appearances and what makes the game 1991 game TaleSpin truly special!

TaleSpin is just one of the six games featured in The Disney Afternoon Collection, available now for PC, Xbox One and PlayStation 4. http://bit.ly/2oJIDpk

Subscribe to the Official Capcom Unity Channel: 
http://bit.ly/Qjb2MV
